comments: Valanciunas (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in Kuminga's (GSW) path and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Kuminga (GSW) places a marginal forearm on Ingram's (NOP) side as he cleanly dislodges the ball at the end of the drive.
Valanciunas (NOP) and Porter Jr. (GSW) mutually engage and separate during the rebound.
Ingram (NOP) moves alongside Kuminga's (GSW) path and makes incidental contact as he contests the driving shot attempt.
Porter Jr. (GSW) places a bent forearm on Jones' (NOP) body and makes marginal contact as he contests the driving shot attempt.
Bjelica (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in Jones' (NOP) path and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
Jones (NOP) slides his hand across and off Lee's (GSW) front off-ball, and the contact is marginal.
Lee (GSW) lifts his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Jones (NOP) has a resting hand on Poole's (GSW) side and removes it as Poole enters his shooting motion.
Lee (GSW) brushes Hart's (NOP) hand that's on the ball and disengages as he releases his pass.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Clark (NOP) is the last person to touch the ball. The possession is correctly awarded to GSW.

Poole (GSW) makes contact with Ingram's (NOP) arm that affects his SQBR.
